OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1782910144
OL,3,CMissing Leeds United superfan
OL,4,Caccidentally found in Barcelona pub
OL,6,FA Leeds United superfan who vanished
OL,7,Fwhen travelling to the USA for the
OL,8,FWorld Cup was accidentally found in a
OL,9,FBarcelona pub and was 'blissfully
OL,10,Funaware the world was looking for him'.
OL,12,FMichael Hewitt, who is known to many
OL,13,Fas 'Little Mick', had been travelling
OL,14,Ffrom Leeds to Boston for the World Cup
OL,15,Fvia Barcelona on Saturday 20 June.
OL,17,FHis family said their last contact
OL,18,Fwith him was a text message when he
OL,19,Fwas in Barcelona in the early hours of
OL,20,FSunday 21 June.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
