PN,33202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1782910144
OL,3,CMissing Leeds United superfan
OL,4,Caccidentally found in Barcelona pub
OL,6,FThey reported him missing as they said
OL,7,FMick's phone had been out of service
OL,8,Fsince then and he hadn't posted any
OL,9,Fupdates on social media.
OL,11,FHis siblings spoke to ITV News
OL,12,FCalendar on Tuesday 30 June sharing
OL,13,Ftheir worries.
OL,15,FMick's brother, Gary Hewitt, said: "He
OL,16,Fvanished without a trace."
OL,18,FThen an off-duty police officer on
OL,19,Fholiday in Barcelona accidentally
OL,20,Ffound him.
OL,26,@xD@ZO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
