OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1782910144
OL,3,CMissing Leeds United superfan
OL,4,Caccidentally found in Barcelona pub
OL,6,FThe pair were both in a pub wearing
OL,7,FLeeds United tops and did a 'Leeds
OL,8,Fsalute' to one another.
OL,10,FThe officer did not realise Mick was a
OL,11,Fmissing man until he returned to his
OL,12,Fhotel, opened up his phone and saw
OL,13,Fposts on social media.
OL,15,FThe officer then went to the police in
OL,16,FBarcelona to report he had found Mick.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
