FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1782910144
OL,3,CMissing Leeds United superfan
OL,4,Caccidentally found in Barcelona pub
OL,6,FGary said they have now learned that
OL,7,FMick had lost his phone so hadn't seen
OL,8,Fany of the missing person posts online
OL,9,Fand didn't realise people were looking
OL,10,Ffor him.
OL,12,FHe said: "Fantastic news! Little Mick
OL,13,Fis safe and well in Barcelona, and was
OL,14,Fblissfully unaware that the world was
OL,15,Fsearching for him!
OL,17,F"As a family, we desperately wanted an
OL,18,Fembarrassingly simple but happy ending
OL,19,Fto this horrendous episode, and we now
OL,20,Fhave that.
OL,26,@tD@JOUyD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
