PN,33205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1782910144
OL,3,CMissing Leeds United superfan
OL,4,Caccidentally found in Barcelona pub
OL,6,F"A million thanks to each and every
OL,7,Fperson who has helped to bring Mick
OL,8,Fhome safely, and for all the good
OL,9,Fwishes."
OL,11,FThe family say what has happened
OL,12,Fhighlights the importance of staying
OL,13,Fin touch as well as the power of
OL,14,Ffootball and the internet.
OL,16,FThough he has been found, Mick won't
OL,17,Fbe returning home right away as he is
OL,18,Fstaying in Barcelona to watch the next
OL,19,FEngland World Cup match!
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@HO]
